        {
            "title": "烏克蘭總統澤連斯基會晤川普後指責歐洲盟友流於空談",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 俄烏戰爭進入第四年之際，烏克蘭在俄羅斯的頻繁轟炸下陷入斷水、斷暖、斷電困境。該國總統<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:澤連斯基;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/澤連斯基\">澤連斯基</a>在達沃斯指責歐洲缺乏阻止普丁的意願。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在周四的演講中，澤連斯基稱歐洲盟友既不能攔截俄羅斯的「影子艦隊」油輪，對沒收凍結的俄羅斯資產也是縮手縮腳，在美國注意力轉向他處時，歐洲缺乏作為真正全球大國採取行動的意志。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「歐洲喜歡討論未來，卻回避在當下採取行動，」一臉憤怒的澤連斯基對台下聽眾說。「那些準備採取行動的領導人都在哪兒？」</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-e52d104f-ff65-3910-9c38-813a4856c804-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這位烏克蘭總統在發表講話前，匆忙趕往達沃斯與川普舉行了一場臨時安排的會晤。川普形容這次會晤是「良好的」，並再次表達了對俄烏戰爭儘早結束的期待。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">澤連斯基在演講中稱，「我們不應接受歐洲只是一個由中小國家拼湊而成、還夾雜著歐洲敵人的‘沙拉’。當烏克蘭與你們並肩時，沒有人敢踐踏你們，你們將永遠擁有採取行動的途徑，而且是及時的行動。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Zelenskiy Slams Europe for Inaction in Countering Putin</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%83%8F%E5%85%8B%E8%98%AD%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E6%BE%A4%E9%80%A3%E6%96%AF%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%83%E6%99%A4%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E5%BE%8C%E6%8C%87%E8%B2%AC%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E7%9B%9F%E5%8F%8B%E6%B5%81%E6%96%BC%E7%A9%BA%E8%AB%87-145959177.html",
