        {
            "title": "達沃斯最高調的批評者馬斯克將首次亮相該論壇 與Fink對談",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 億萬富豪埃隆·<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:馬斯克;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/馬斯克\">馬斯克</a>將首次亮相<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:達沃斯;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/達沃斯\">達沃斯</a>世界經濟論壇。多年來，他一直對該年會頗為不滿。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">已確認馬斯克是周四下午一場活動的臨時新增嘉賓，將與貝萊德執行長Larry Fink對談。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這位特斯拉、SpaceX和xAI的執行長現身達沃斯，標志著他與論壇之間的關係出現變化。每年1月，達沃斯都會吸引各國領導人、億萬富豪及全球媒體齊聚在瑞士。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">去年馬斯克也收到了邀請，但並未前往。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">馬斯克過去曾稱這場全球精英的年度聚會「無聊」，並抨擊世界經濟論壇正「越來越變成一個不經選舉產生的世界政府 —— 人民既沒有要求，也不想要」。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-746df499-654e-3bc0-92cd-7df23cd772d5-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">馬斯克2022年曾在他的社交媒體平台X上發帖稱：「WEF/達沃斯怎麼算得了一回事？他們是想當‘整個地球的老板’嗎！？」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Musk, Davos’ Most High-Profile Hater, to Make First Appearance</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Chad Thomas.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%81%94%E6%B2%83%E6%96%AF%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E8%AA%BF%E7%9A%84%E6%89%B9%E8%A9%95%E8%80%85%E9%A6%AC%E6%96%AF%E5%85%8B%E5%B0%87%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E4%BA%AE%E7%9B%B8%E8%A9%B2%E8%AB%96%E5%A3%87-%E8%88%87fink%E5%B0%8D%E8%AB%87-121715887.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-22 22:09:39",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "川普稱如果歐洲拋售美國資產 他將有「重大報復行動」",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國總統唐納德·川普承諾，如果歐洲國家賣出美國資產以因應他的關稅威脅，他將有「重大報復行動」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「如果他們真這麼做，那就做吧。但如果真發生這種事，我方會有重大報復行動，」川普周四在達沃斯世界經濟論壇期間接受福克斯商業新聞頻道採訪時說。「我們手上握著所有的牌。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">丹麥養老基金AkademikerPension本周宣布，計畫賣出1億美元美國國債；格陵蘭的SISA養老金公司也表示，正在考慮是否應繼續投資美國股票。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-8bf488b3-3cbe-3eeb-a18a-a94ba9a81f93-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國財政部長斯科特·貝森特本周早些時候淡化了丹麥方面的出售行動，稱自己「完全不擔心」。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「丹麥對美國國債的投資，就像丹麥本身一樣，無關緊要，」貝森特周三在達沃斯表示。「他們賣美國國債已經賣了很多年。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Trump Threatens ‘Big Retaliation’ If Europe Dumps US Assets</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Greg Ritchie.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E7%A8%B1%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E6%8B%8B%E5%94%AE%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%B3%87%E7%94%A2-%E4%BB%96%E5%B0%87%E6%9C%89-%E9%87%8D%E5%A4%A7%E5%A0%B1%E5%BE%A9%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95-135949986.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-22 22:49:48",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "達利歐：市場一直在分散資產配置、減少對美國資產的依賴",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 對沖基金橋水的創始人瑞·<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:達利歐;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/達利歐\">達利歐</a>表示，市場一直在持續地整體上分散資產配置、減少對美國資產的依賴，尤其是全球各國的中央銀行。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「你看黃金上漲了67%，上漲60%的並不是貴金屬本身，」達利歐周四在達沃斯接受彭博電視台主持人Francine Lacqua採訪時表示。「主要是中央銀行，也包括其他買家買入，從而分散對法定貨幣的配置，不僅僅是美元。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在談及全球緊張局勢時，達利歐表示，外界把大量注意力放在貿易戰上，但對他所說的「資本戰」及其對市場的影響關注很少。談到美國總統唐納德·川普在謀求獲得格陵蘭時排除動用軍事力量的說法，達利歐稱此番講話「非常重要，因為存在一條界線，一條紅線」。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-ab1f2ab1-776b-356f-8f46-85ba33b106f2-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「如果發生軍事行動，就會帶來資本戰層面的影響，」達利歐表示。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Ray Dalio Sees Ongoing Diversification Away From US Assets</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%81%94%E5%88%A9%E6%AD%90-%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4-%E7%9B%B4%E5%9C%A8%E5%88%86%E6%95%A3%E8%B3%87%E7%94%A2%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE-%E6%B8%9B%E5%B0%91%E5%B0%8D%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%B3%87%E7%94%A2%E7%9A%84%E4%BE%9D%E8%B3%B4-114453574.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-22 20:46:31",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "潘功勝稱今年降準降息還有一定空間 將靈活高效運用多種貨幣政策工具",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 中國人民銀行行長<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:潘功勝;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/潘功勝\">潘功勝</a>暗示，仍有進一步降息並向銀行體系注入流動性的空間，與他的副手在上周給出的指引一致，即2026年將繼續實施支持性的貨幣政策。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">潘功勝在接受新華社採訪時表示，在總量政策方面，將「靈活高效運用降準降息等多種貨幣政策工具」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他表示，「今年降準降息還有一定的空間。人民銀行還將做好利率政策執行和監督，促進社會綜合融資成本低位運行。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國人民銀行此前的政策利率下調幅度未達經濟學家預期，一直試圖安撫市場情緒。儘管出口表現堅挺，但中國經濟仍面臨持續通縮和信心的疲軟。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-6ee97702-d62c-3a37-9b83-c29b707d358b-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">潘功勝指出，今年央行已下調各類結構性貨幣政策工具利率0.25個百分點，並單設1萬億元民營企業再貸款，合併設立科技創新與民營企業債券風險分擔工具。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他還重申，要做好預期管理，保持人民幣匯率在合理均衡水平上的基本穩定；建立在特定情景下向非銀機構提供流動性的機制性安排。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題PBOC’s Pan Reaffirms Room for Further Easing to Support Growth</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%BD%98%E5%8A%9F%E5%8B%9D%E7%A8%B1%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E9%99%8D%E6%BA%96%E9%99%8D%E6%81%AF%E9%82%84%E6%9C%89-%E5%AE%9A%E7%A9%BA%E9%96%93-%E5%B0%87%E9%9D%88%E6%B4%BB%E9%AB%98%E6%95%88%E9%81%8B%E7%94%A8%E5%A4%9A%E7%A8%AE%E8%B2%A8%E5%B9%A3%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7-113112867.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-22 20:04:45",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "台幣置身於全球市場震盪之外 大型出口商與公股銀行扮演穩盤角色",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 正當全球金融市場因地緣政治緊張情緒波動放大之際，近日<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:台幣;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/台幣\">台幣</a>尚能維持穩定於小幅區間，且兩周期的歷史波動率在主要亞幣裡僅高於港元與人民幣，主因本地匯市的美元供、需動態平衡。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據多位外匯交易員表示，在本周二與周三外資匯出主導台幣貶值，日內跌幅擴大之際，看到大型出口商賣出美元與外資對作，達到限制台幣貶勢的作用，公股銀行則於尾盤流動性較低的時候繼續賣出美元，進一步收斂台幣貶幅。而通常當市場參與者看見一家大型出口商大量賣出美元後，買入美元/台幣的報價就不再繼續上行。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-bcc8cd6f-b723-39ef-a2e1-760ebf51d434-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/EHBhZaW5hvwIdttYeAGkKA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/824943d02e7a1029cdc764f9300c15f7\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">反之當台幣走勢偏升時美元買盤也會伺機出沒。其中一位交易員稱，上周當外資匯入較多時, 亦看到壽險業的美元買盤出籠。上述交易員不願具名接受採訪，因未被授權公開評論。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據彭博數據，台幣一個月期隱含波動度於周四降至逾9個月新低，與其他亞幣波動度升高的情況逆勢而行。另外，就兩周期的主要亞幣歷史波動率來觀察，台幣只高於定錨美元的港元，以及受到較多監管的人民幣。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">台幣兌美元在最近10個交易日裡陷於31.494-31.706的區間拉鋸，穩定走勢反映出，儘管外資進出仍是匯率走勢的主導因素，但具指標性的市場參與者的行為可以有效使匯價免於過度波動。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國銀行於報告指出，美元供需平衡的狀態使得台幣目前相對穩定，預期第一季將延續低波動的態勢，不過任何來自於美國財政部對於台幣估值過低的評論為潛在風險。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8F%B0%E5%B9%A3%E7%BD%AE%E8%BA%AB%E6%96%BC%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E9%9C%87%E7%9B%AA%E4%B9%8B%E5%A4%96-%E5%A4%A7%E5%9E%8B%E5%87%BA%E5%8F%A3%E5%95%86%E8%88%87%E5%85%AC%E8%82%A1%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E6%89%AE%E6%BC%94%E7%A9%A9%E7%9B%A4%E8%A7%92%E8%89%B2-081409014.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-22 16:54:55",
