            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "亮出抗議姿態 格陵蘭養老基金考慮是否繼續投資美股",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"551\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/keWPPl7R0VY3znKfnTt4eg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU1MQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/2fd47b441bd0c4c8288292935afe95dc\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 格陵蘭養老基金正在考慮是否繼續投資美國股票。該基金執行長表示，此舉將是對美國總統唐納德·川普企圖控制這座北極島嶼具有象征意義的抗議。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">管理著約70億丹麥克朗（11億美元）資產的SISA養老基金，目前約50%的投資配置在美國市場，主要為公開上市股票。執行長Søren Schock Petersen在接受採訪時表示，雖然尚未做出決定，但董事會和投資委員會一直在討論是否有必要撤資。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我們仍在討論此事，並將繼續討論。未來某個時候，我們可能會說夠了，」駐哥本哈根的Petersen通過電話表示。「這種持續的壓力最終可能會導致我們必須採取行動，不能再繼續忽視它。」</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-2e5c1e6c-1ab5-3591-a0fd-dbee5a1df84f-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普威脅對反對其控制格陵蘭島計畫的歐洲國家加徵關稅後，本周關於外國投資者拋售美國資產的討論再度升溫。但川普周三撤回了關稅計畫，稱「就該島達成未來協議框架」。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Petersen最初發表言論時川普尚未緩和立場，但Petersen隨後表示，他堅持此前關於該基金重新評估其美國投資的表態。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"551\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/OXzEvxAKPbfs4LroQtgzog--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU1MQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/bc2f6137378b533d04acf17ed5014c2d\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">若該格陵蘭養老基金決定拋售美國資產，鑒於美國股市的頭號地位，這將是一個驚人的轉變。MSCI World指數中約70%由美國股票構成，其近幾十年的優異表現助長了「美國例外論」。對幾乎所有人而言，這個市場都大得不容忽視。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Greenland Pension Fund Mulls Divesting US Stocks on Trump Threat</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Michael Msika、Sara Sjolin.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BA%AE%E5%87%BA%E6%8A%97%E8%AD%B0%E5%A7%BF%E6%85%8B-%E6%A0%BC%E9%99%B5%E8%98%AD%E9%A4%8A%E8%80%81%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E7%B9%BC%E7%BA%8C%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E7%BE%8E%E8%82%A1-110949996.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-22 20:04:50",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "泡泡瑪特股價大漲 新華社對公司CEO的採訪即將播出",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:泡泡瑪特;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/泡泡瑪特\">泡泡瑪特</a>股價午後大幅上漲，中國官媒對該公司執行長王寧的採訪即將播出，提振了投資者情緒。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">泡泡瑪特香港上市的股票一度上漲6.8%，此前騰訊視頻紀錄片在微博賬號上宣布，新華社對泡泡瑪特執行長的採訪將於周五中午12點播出。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Nqvc3HrGneosH5Nt4t42CA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/08eaee6caf30e82185d14a82809480d6\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本周泡泡瑪特的股價已反彈逾15%，該公司此前自2024年以來首次回購股票。自周一以來，泡泡瑪特已累計回購3.47億港元（4500萬美元）的股票。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：泡泡瑪特創近兩個月來盤中最大漲幅 公司自2024年初來首次回購股份</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-1fd04bba-78be-3108-a828-2dee7947c90b-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Pop Mart Shares Rally as Investors Look to CEO’s Interview</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Jing Jin.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B3%A1%E6%B3%A1%E7%91%AA%E7%89%B9%E8%82%A1%E5%83%B9%E5%A4%A7%E6%BC%B2-%E6%96%B0%E8%8F%AF%E7%A4%BE%E5%B0%8D%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8ceo%E7%9A%84%E6%8E%A1%E8%A8%AA%E5%8D%B3%E5%B0%87%E6%92%AD%E5%87%BA-075022396.html",
